Package com.softwareag.natural.mapconverter.logger Description

Contains classes to write map conversion logfiles.

Map Conversion Logfiles

This package contains classes to write map conversion logfiles. When extending the conversion process with custom classes the custom classes can add their own logging entries via using the MapConverterLogger class of this package.
